    Calculates Euclidean distance and performs t-SNE

    EuclideanDistance.Rd

    This function computes the Euclidean distance matrix from the input dataset, normalizes it, and applies t-SNE for dimensionality reduction.

    EuclideanDistance(ptmtable)

    Arguments

    ptmtable

    A data frame containing numeric data for post-translational modifications.

    Value

    A matrix containing t-SNE coordinates (3D).

    Examples

    EuclideanDistance(ptmtable)
